news.title: NGT directs Pune civic body, MPCB to file replies on dumping construction debris on riverbanks
news.para: The responses are to be filed before the green tribunal’s western zonal bench, Pune, which will take over the hearing of the matter from September 11.

news.title: UP-RERA orders Noida, Greater Noida authorities and 18 builders to appear in online hearings
news.para: Complaints related to Gautam Buddh Nagar-bench belong to Satya Homes, Divyanka Homes, NOIDA, Greater NOIDA, Logix Infra Developers, Ashoka Priyansh Builders, Shamiah International Builders, Syore Infraprojects, VXL Realtors and one more.

news.title: Government may reduce income cap for PMAY homes in urban areas
news.para: Although officials are tight-lipped about the interest subsidy for MIG beneficiaries, sources said it may be around Rs 2.6 lakh as was provided in the last phase of the scheme.

news.title: Mumbai: 540 acres of suburban land identified to shift Dharavi's 'ineligible' residents
news.para: The Dharavi Redevelopment Project Ltd (DRPPL), a 80:20 joint venture between the Adani group and state govt, is building free housing – in-situ – for residents of tenements that have been in existence in Dharavi from before 2000.

news.title: SC orders no coercive action to be taken against NCR homebuyers
news.para: Under the subvention scheme, banks disburse the sanctioned amount directly to the accounts of builders, who are then to pay EMIs on the sanctioned loan amount until possession of the flats is handed over to the homebuyers.

news.title: Mumbai police book Shriji developers' directors for cheating
news.para: The project was supposed to be completed by 2021, but Shah discovered that the developer had sold the project to Ruparel Reality instead.

news.title: Hyderabad: Bhavishya Realtors & NSA Avenue booked for duping buyers
news.para: CCS sleuths booked the case against Bhavishya Realtors and NSA Avenue Private Ltd for criminal conspiracy and concealing the facts, based on a complaint by Surabhi Ashok Rao, 56, of Dulapally.

news.title: KL Rahul & Athiya Shetty buy flat in Mumbai’s Pali Hill for over Rs 20 crore
news.para: The couple has bought the apartment spread over a carpet area of 3,350 sq ft in the tower Sandhu Palace from the developer Sandhu Builders.

news.title: Supply in Canada's property market surges as mortgage renewals loom
news.para: In Toronto, a city where two-thirds of the country's condominiums are sold, considered a bellwether for other big metropolitan areas, inventories have pushed past highs reached 10 years ago, data showed. At the same time, sales have lagged.

news.title: House prices in Ireland increase by 8.2% in May 2024
news.para: The national index has now reached a value of 179.4, which is 9.7% above its highest level at the peak of the property boom in April 2007.

news.title: Asian Paints' profit declines 24.6% to Rs 1,186.79 crore in Q1 FY25
news.para: Consolidated revenue from operations in the first quarter of the current fiscal was down at Rs 8,969.73 crore as compared to Rs 9,182.31 crore in the year-ago period, it added.

news.title: Hong Kong posts record home purchases by mainland Chinese: Centaline Property Agency
news.para: In late February, Hong Kong removed all additional stamp duties for foreign and second home buyers, as well as on those selling flats within two years of buying them, after prices had plunged 20% from their 2021 peak.

news.title: DLF's chairman receives Rs 27.3 crore as remuneration for FY24
news.para: In the latest GROHE-Hurun list released recently, the 65-year-old Singh is the richest real estate entrepreneur, having a wealth of Rs 1,24,420 crore. Among real estate firms, DLF secured the top spot with a valuation of Rs 2 lakh crore.

news.title: Alphacorp to invest Rs 350 crore to develop housing project in Gurugram
news.para: On one parcel of 2.38 acre, the company has launched luxury high-rise project 'Alphacorp SKY1' comprising 100 units. The price is Rs 5 crore per unit. The project on the second plot will also be launched in the next 2-3 months

news.title: Corvi LED raises $8 million in series B round led by Enam Investments
news.para: The funds will be mainly used to scale up operations and make substantial investments in marketing and distribution to strengthen the company's market presence in B2C and B2B segments.

news.title: Housing layout threatens Visakhapatnam's geological heritage site
news.para: Erra Matti Dibbalu on the shores of Bay of Bengal on Bheemili beach road in Vizag city are facing the threat of disintegration due to official apathy.

news.title: Altern Capital launches Rs 250 crore real estate focused fund
news.para: The target size of this fund is Rs 250 crore, with an additional greenshoe option of Rs 100 crore. AI Growth is the sponsor of JIREF I.

news.title: RLDA invites bids to redevelop a railway colony in Delhi
news.para: The land, with an approximate area of 2.156 hectares (21,568.35 sq meters), will be leased for 99 years with a reserve price of Rs 318 crore. The site has an applicable floor area ratio (FAR) of 16,176.26 sq meters.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh cabinet scraps Land Titling act, approves free sand distribution
news.para: ​​​​Information and Public Relations Minister K Parthasarathy said the cabinet scrapped the Andhra Pradesh Land Titling Act, 2022, passed during the erstwhile YSRCP government, as it was allegedly beset with several issues.
